
hs - a reverse sh
-----------------

Usage: hs [--cmd|-c <cmd>]       (Client Mode)
          [--remote|-r <dest>]
          [--port|-p <port>]
          [--daemon|-d]
          [--key|-k <key>]
          [--loop|-l]
          [--wait|-w <secs>]
          [--attempts|-a <n>]
          [--interval|-i <secs>]
          [--timeout|-t <secs>]
       hs --server|-s            (Server Mode)
          [--port|-p <port>]
          [--key|-k <key>]
          [--loop|-l]
          [--timeout|-t <secs>]
       hs [--help|-h]
